OL,6,FMore than 800 miles from the
OL,7,Fepicentre, in Bangkok, a high-rise
OL,8,Fbuilding under construction came
OL,9,Fcrashing down, killing at least three
OL,10,Fpeople and burying dozens more beneath
OL,11,Fthe rubble.
OL,13,FThailand's Department of Disaster
OL,14,FPrevention said the quake was felt in
OL,15,Falmost all areas of the country.
OL,17,FTo the northeast, the earthquake was
OL,18,Ffelt in China and caused damage to
OL,19,Fhouses and injuries in the city of
OL,20,FRuili on the border with Myanmar,
OL,21,Faccording to Chinese media reports.
