OL,6,FWhile the severity of the disaster is
OL,7,Fstill unfolding, the scale is
OL,8,Fundeniable, with rescue efforts
OL,9,Funderway across multiple countries.
OL,11,FHere, ITV News explains why this
OL,12,Fearthquake caused such widespread
OL,13,Fdestruction and how the impact of the
OL,14,Fdisaster is measured.
OL,16,FWhat is a shallow earthquake and why
OL,17,Fare they so dangerous?
OL,19,FMyanmar's earthquake was so powerful
OL,20,Fbecause it was shallow - occurring
OL,21,Fjust 10km below the Earth's surface.
