OL,3,CWhat is a shallow earthquake and why
OL,4,Care they so dangerous?
OL,6,FShallow earthquakes tend to happen on
OL,7,Fmid-ocean ridges and transform
OL,8,Fmargins..
OL,10,FMyanmar lies along a major fault line,
OL,11,Fwhich is the boundary where tectonic
OL,12,Fplates meet.
OL,14,FThe Indian plate is slowly pushing
OL,15,Finto the Eurasian plate, building up
OL,16,Fenormous pressure underground.
